Source:  Empire of the Dairy Farmers
Author:  YEREX
Vol / Page:  116
Edition:
Quote:  The process of removing cups from cows on one side of the pit and transferring them to those on the orher side was developed to the status of an art form known as 'the herringbone waltz.'
